snippet: The two-time United States Open champion Lee Janzen was knocked out of this year’s qualifying for wearing metal spikes at a golf course that does not allow them.
lead_paragraph: The two-time United States Open champion Lee Janzen was knocked out of this year’s qualifying for wearing metal spikes at a golf course that does not allow them.
